 
The following topics may be useful in clarifying rules or 
providing information on those subjects. Ignorance of the
rules is not an excuse. Either 'cat /doc/w/<topic>' or
'man <topic>'.
 
topic             description
---------------   -----------------------------------------------
wiz_banishment    Explanation of banishment of wizards
wiz_demotion      For those wizards who want to be players again
wiz_interaction   Some rules for wizards interacting with players
wiz_players       Rules for wizards having players
wiz_tools         Rules about wizard tools
 
